    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into wedges and slice the <strong>rested chipotle steak[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced chipotle steak </strong>over the<strong> creamed corn </strong>with the<strong> potato wedges </strong>and<strong> roasted courgette</strong> <strong>& tomato</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the sliced chipotle steak with the <strong>remaining chipotle butter</strong>, sprinkle over the <strong>reserved herbs</strong> and garnish with the <strong>lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
